title: Notomulciber quadrimaculatus
summary: Notomulciber quadrimaculatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning and de Jong in 1941. It is known from Borneo.
content:
Notomulciber quadrimaculatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning and de Jong in 1941. It is known from Borneo.
